25
00:01:36,306 --> 00:01:39,726
Who do you think I am...

26
00:01:40,059 --> 00:01:43,062
Expelled from Osaka
for killing a man,

27
00:01:43,187 --> 00:01:44,939
I'm Senkichi of Kotetsu!

28
00:01:45,064 --> 00:01:46,983
Here's your dagger.

29
00:01:47,233 --> 00:01:51,070
