turbulent waves breaking.

71
00:06:18,004 --> 00:06:22,341
My mother was deceived
by my father,

72
00:06:22,633 --> 00:06:24,510
who was a Ronin.

73
00:06:26,387 --> 00:06:30,016
She could never return
to her native Osaka,

74
00:06:32,143 --> 00:06:34,520
