Orin.

1649
02:23:32,647 --> 02:23:34,398
My bet...

1650
02:23:35,483 --> 02:23:38,528
I might have lost it...

1651
02:23:41,781 --> 02:23:43,032
Senkichi-san.

1652
02:23:51,165 --> 02:23:54,168
Gionmachi was intact. Come!

1653
02:23:54,377 --> 02:23:55,795
With your precious...

1654
02:23:57,672 --> 02:23:59,006
If Kotaro,

1655
